<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<Defs>

  <ThingDef ParentName="MechSerumBase">
    <defName>CarbuncleGem</defName>
    <label>carbuncle gem</label>
    <description>온전한 카벙클보석, 높은 가치를 가지고 있으며, 행운을 불러온다고 합니다.</description>
    <graphicData>
      <texPath>Things/Item/Special/CarbuncleGem</texPath>
      <graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
	  <drawSize>0.75</drawSize>
    </graphicData>
    <stackLimit>10</stackLimit>
    <statBases>
      <MarketValue>1200</MarketValue>
	  <Beauty>50</Beauty>
    </statBases>
    <thingCategories>
      <li>Items</li>
    </thingCategories>
    <tradeability>Sellable</tradeability>
    <thingSetMakerTags>
      <li>RewardStandardMidFreq</li>
    </thingSetMakerTags>
    <comps>
      <li Class="CompProperties_Usable">
        <useJob>UseItem</useJob>
        <useLabel>carbuncle gem</useLabel>
        <useDuration>0</useDuration>
      </li>
      <li Class="CompProperties_Targetable">
        <compClass>CompTargetable_SingleCorpse</compClass>
        <fleshCorpsesOnly>true</fleshCorpsesOnly>
        <nonDessicatedCorpsesOnly>true</nonDessicatedCorpsesOnly>
      </li>
      <li>
        <compClass>CompTargetEffect_Resurrect</compClass>
      </li>
    </comps>
  </ThingDef>


  <ThingDef ParentName="ResourceVerbBase">
    <defName>UnicornHorn</defName>
    <label>unicorn horn</label>
    <description>아름다운 유니콘의 뿔입니다. 알리콘이라는 성분으로 이루어져 있으며, 이것으로 만든 약의 효과는 번화계에서도 알려져 있습니다.</description>
    <graphicData>
      <texPath>Things/Item/Special/UnicornHorn</texPath>
      <graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
    </graphicData>
    <equippedAngleOffset>-20</equippedAngleOffset>
    <statBases>
      <MarketValue>1000</MarketValue>
      <MaxHitPoints>125</MaxHitPoints>
      <Mass>0.9</Mass>
      <Flammability>0.1</Flammability>
      <DeteriorationRate>0.01</DeteriorationRate>
    </statBases>
    <resourceReadoutPriority>Middle</resourceReadoutPriority>
    <stackLimit>10</stackLimit>
    <tools>
      <li>
        <label>point</label>
        <capacities>
          <li>Scratch</li>
          <li>Stab</li>
        </capacities>
        <power>21.8</power>
        <cooldownTime>2.6</cooldownTime>
      </li>
      <li>
        <label>base</label>
        <capacities>
          <li>Blunt</li>
        </capacities>
        <power>9</power>
        <cooldownTime>2</cooldownTime>
        <chanceFactor>0.5</chanceFactor>
      </li>
    </tools>
    <thingCategories>
      <li>Items</li>
    </thingCategories>
    <tradeTags>
      <li>ExoticMisc</li>
    </tradeTags>
    <thingSetMakerTags>
      <li>AnimalPart</li>
    </thingSetMakerTags>
  </ThingDef>

</Defs>
